            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Senatus <lb n="2"/>populusque Romanus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Caesari Divi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Augusto <lb n="4"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> VIII dedit clupeum <lb n="5"/>virtutis clementiae <lb n="6"/>iustitiae pietatis erga <lb n="7"/>deos patriamque
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Clipeus virtutis.</p>
            </div>
